{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3a5a2955-bf89-4a9b-8a9d-b2840f3c3048","content":"I can help point you in the right direction, though I don't have a specialized skill for **dump analysis** (only for dump *collection*).\n\nHere's how to analyze a `.dmp` file from a .NET app:\n\n**Using `dotnet-dump analyze`** (cross-platform):\n```bash\ndotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump\ndotnet-dump analyze your-file.dmp\n```\nUseful SOS commands inside the interactive session:\n| Command | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `clrstack` | Managed call stack |\n| `pe` (`printexception`) | Last exception details |\n| `dumpheap -stat` | Heap summary |\n| `threads` | List all threads |\n| `setthread <id>` + `clrstack` | Stack for a specific thread |\n\n**Using LLDB (Linux):**\n```bash\ndotnet-dump analyze your-file.dmp\n# or\nlldb --core your-file.dmp -o \"plugin load libsosplugin.so\"\n```\n\n**Using WinDbg (Windows):**\nLoad the dump, then use `!analyze -v` and `!clrstack`.\n\n**Typical workflow to find root cause:**\n1. `pe` — check if an unhandled exception caused the crash\n2. `threads` — find the faulting thread\n3. `setthread <id>` → `clrstack` — inspect its stack\n4. `dumpobj <addr>` — examine objects on the stack\n\nWould you like help with any specific step, or do you have the dump file accessible here so I can run `dotnet-dump analyze` on it?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2d67daf1-3c46-4674-8460-26fea90dbc4d","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about analyzing a .dmp crash dump file. Let me check the available skills - there's a `dump-collect` skill, but its description specifically says:\n\n- USE FOR: enabling automatic crash dumps, capturing dumps, setting up dump collection\n- DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze\n\nSo the dump-collect skill is not appropriate here. The user needs help with dump *analysis*, not collection.\n\nLet me provide guidance on how to analyze a .NET crash dump.","outputTokens":526,"requestId":"4191:2C3A9C:649ED99:6DE2157:69F164E1"},"id":"08aa6f45-4408-4032-a28d-ce7b0147aa21","timestamp":"2026-04-29T01:55:26.000Z","parentId":"1eb2d6fe-3d42-4c9d-a22c-dafa948739dc"}
